PH\u1ede TH\u1ed0 \u0110&Aacute;<\/h2>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute;left: 294px;top: -9.66193px\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\">&nbsp;<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><\/h1><div class=\"ffb-id-4u1l4i1h fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-center text-sm-center text-md-center text-lg-center fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">V\u1edbi c&ocirc;ng th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng \u0111&atilde; \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn v&agrave; y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch t\u1ea1i Caravelle S&agrave;i G&ograve;n t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1959, B\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i \u0111&atilde; n&acirc;ng m&oacute;n Ph\u1edf truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng l&ecirc;n m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng c&aacute;ch b\u1ed5 sung th&ecirc;m t\u1ee7y x\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111&agrave;, \u0111u&ocirc;i b&ograve; \u0111\u1eadm \u0111&agrave; v&agrave; th\u1ecbt m\u1ec1m trong B&aacute;t \u0110&aacute; N&oacute;ng. mang l\u1ea1i tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">H&atilde;y th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c m&oacute;n Ph\u1edf B&aacute;t \u0110&aacute; N&oacute;ng \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111&aacute;o c\u1ee7a ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i - n\u01b0\u1edbc d&ugrave;ng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111&agrave;, b&uacute;n \u0111\u1eadm \u0111&agrave;, rau th\u01a1m v&agrave; nh\u1eefng l&aacute;t th\u1ecbt b&ograve; m\u1ecdng n\u01b0\u1edbc k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhau trong s\u1ef1 h&ograve;a h\u1ee3p \u1ea9m th\u1ef1c ho&agrave;n h\u1ea3o trong t&ocirc; \u0111&aacute; n&oacute;ng, mang \u0111\u1ebfn c&aacute;i nh&igrave;n \u0111\u1ea7y m&ecirc; ho\u1eb7c v\u1ec1 ngh\u1ec7 thu\u1eadt h&ograve;a tr\u1ed9n h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* Caravelle Ph\u1edf ch\u1ec9 t\u1eeb \u200b\u200b259.000 VN\u0110++<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* H&agrave;ng ng&agrave;y, t\u1eeb 7:00 - 22:00<\/p>\n<p><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-5ggirhco buttons-el-wrapper text-center